item.title: My New Sig
item.dc:creator: @ThAt0n36Uy Elijah
item.description:
@ThAt0n36Uy wrote:

There’s to much going on in the image. I am drawn to the text the most. Which isn’t a good thing. The render just reminds me of a terrible TV show I once watched a few years ago. And it just doesn’t have any meaning. It’s as if you just took a picture and placed some color balance layers over a signature and slapped some text on it. I like how you attempted to take other images and text and put them in the background.

It shows you have somewhat of an idea as to what you’re doing. You’re getting there, that’s for sure. You just need some tutorials. I suggest a couple Tag tutorials, an Abstract tutorial, and a brushing tutorial, as well as a Text Effect tutorial.
